data.description: This is a move-in ready 1-1/2 story home which has been meticulously maintained and nicely updated. First floor features an eat-in kitchen and lots of cupboards, a formal dining room, and a large living room with custom bookshelves. First floor also features two beautiful bedrooms with custom closets. Between the bedrooms is a full bath and large hallway closets for storage. Upstairs you have 2 additional bedrooms with large closets and a 3/4th bath. Laundry is located on the first floor. Home is nicely updated with vinyl siding, metal roof, updated electric, and central air. Outside you will find a covered back porch overlooking a fenced back yard. Attached garage and concrete drive complete this solid home.
